VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT resource\s+"aws_db_instance"[^}]*multi_az\s*=\s*false
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:multi_az\s*=\s*false && MISSING:# intentional|# development|# staging|# cost
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects production RDS instances with Multi-AZ failover disabled.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for RDS Multi-AZ Disabled.
